<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
      .certificate-link { display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px
      20px; color: white; background-color: #28a745; text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer; }
      .certificate-link:hover { background-color: #218838; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Thank You for {{role}}, {{name}}!</h1>
    <p>
      We truly appreciate your participation in
      <strong>{{event}}</strong>, themed -
      <i>{{theme}}</i>. Your involvement was invaluable, and we are pleased to
      provide you with a certificate recognizing your participation.
    </p>
    <p>
      Click the button below to download your participation certificate:
    </p>
    <a
      class="certificate-link"
      href="{{certificateUrl}}"
      download="{{name}}_certificate.png"
    >View Certificate</a>
    <p>Best regards,<br /> The Event Team</p>
  </body>
</html>